window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Sam was surfing with his cat when the world ended.</b></p> <p>Suddenly enlisted into a battle to fend off annihilation, Sam seizes the strength of the void to survive.</p> <p>In the aftermath, Sam is thrown into a new world shattered into floating islands with survivors from Earth. Training and fighting with his giant sword and apocalyptic mana alongside his magical healer cat, Sam's unusually quick to adapt to this deadly realm of monsters and magic.</p> <p>With endless threats to face and countless powers to attain, Sam's journey of ascension climbing has only just begun.</p> <p>But first, he'll have to forge a legend of his own.</p> <p><i>Blending slice-of-life with epic fantasy action, cultivation, mystery, layer/tower climbing, dungeon delving, kingdom building, and intricate magic systems, this LitRPG/GameLit series is a perfect fit for listeners who enjoy exploring richly detailed worlds, complex characters, and an ever-evolving struggle for the protagonists to make a home in their new world.</i></p>"; 
